OL,6,FITV Wales' Political Editor has the
OL,7,Flatest following Thursday's meeting in
OL,8,FLondon.
OL,10,FAn alternative plan put forward by
OL,11,Ftrade unions trying to save thousands
OL,12,Fof jobs at the steel plan has been
OL,13,Frejected by Tata, according to the
OL,14,FCommunity union.
